high_descs: Turn to the left and go to the sink that is on the right.
Pick up the yellow handled knife to the right of the sink.
Turn around, go to the table, hang a left and go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Cut the tomato that is on the counter into slices.
Turn around, go across the room to the fridge.
Put the knife inside the fridge.
Turn around, go to the counter that is left of the stove.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn around, go across the room to the fridge.
Put the tomato in the fridge and close the door, remove the tomato from the fridge once it is cold.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left and go to the microwave above the sink.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put cold tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the right side of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the right edge of the sink.
Turn around and go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Go to the fridge with the knife.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Go back to the counter left of the stove.
Pick up a tomato slice on the counter.
Take the tomato slice to the fridge.
Chill the tomato slice in the fridge.
Take the cold tomato slice to the microwave.
Put the tomato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left, walk straight, turn right to the sink
Pick up the knife on the sink
Turn right, turn right, walk straight, turn left, walk straight to the counter
Slice the tomato on the counter
Turn right, turn right, walk straight to the fridge
Open the fridge, put the knife inside, close the fridge
Turn right, turn right, walk straight to the counter
Pick up a slice of tomato on top of the counter
Turn right, turn right, walk straight to the fridge
Open the fridge, put the slice of tomato inside, close the fridge. Open the fridge, take out the slice of tomato, close the fridge.
Turn right, walk straight, turn left to the sink
Open the microwave above the sink, put the slice in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of tomato inside a microwave
